data.description: This exceptional home located in vistancia, Arizona's number one master planned community, offering golf courses, pools, hiking trails and parks. This beautiful 5 bedroom, 4.5 bath home with casita has a resort like backyard with mountains views!! It features a large pool and spa, with 1500 sqft of travertine, paver fire pit with pergola, putting green and artificial grass. The interior of this home has too many upgrades to list, but here are a few: central vacuum, plantation shutters throughout, dining room, living room, movie room with surround sound, gourmet kitchen features upgraded cabinets, Butler's pantry with wine fridge, SS appliances and large island with granite countertops.
